input: Subject: A graceful ballerina; Characteristics: mid-dance pose with flowing tutu; Timing and lighting: spotlight on stage; Background: an empty theater; Feeling: elegant and passionate.
output: A graceful ballerina, poised mid-dance in a billowing white tutu, stands bathed in the warm glow of a single spotlight illuminating the vast emptiness of the theater stage. Her every movement is captured in fluid grace as she spins, evoking both elegance and passionate intensity within the hushed silence of the darkened auditorium, leaving the viewer in awe of her captivating performance.
